{
  "stem": "2723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We tried to find some suitable place for the three-- four of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My aunt was always with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother's sister was a polio victim as a child-- had a very bad limp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was my mother's constant companion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So four of us had to find a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that seemed totally impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The bank where my aunt worked offered to hide two people in their vaults.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My aunt and my mother were the ones that were suggested to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My mother and that family counsel felt it might be easier to split and to hide my sister and me somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a strange thing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The janitor of the building where we actually lived, who was like-- I suppose the definition would be a [GERMAN], which meant he affiliated with the Germans-- was so good natured that he persuaded his rather less good natured wife to consider taking us in for no payment, to hide us.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, time frame was something nobody thought of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And perhaps if he had known fully the risk factor-- he wasn't a very smart fellow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a janitor all his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And maybe he-- he didn't think it through very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because our house was confiscated by the German Wehrmacht as soon as they came into Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a significantly more beautiful house than average.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they knew what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was a duel risk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were supposed to be in the lion's den.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And possibly that might have been a better hiding place, but also terribly risky.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So until the very last moment, which I think was sometime end of July, August we didn't--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of 1944-- we didn't really make use of this.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
